content:
Show the Emoji Keyboard in Messaging for Web

Choose to allow messaging for web customers to send emoji to agents in messaging conversations. On the Embedded Service Deployment Settings page, turn on the keyboard.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience. View required editions

USER PERMISSIONS
To set up this feature:
Customize Application
AND
Modify Metadata Through Metadata API Functions

To modify permission sets and profiles: Manage Profiles and Permission Sets

From Setup, enter Embedded Service Deployments, select it, click Edit Settings, select Show Emoji Keyboard, save your changes, publish your deployment.
title: Show Emoji Keyboard in Service Cloud Messaging for Web
